<HEADLINE>
<P>
STALLONE'S STARDOM 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I've been reading Calendar for 15 years and never before was I so moved as by 
the sadness, complexity and innocence of Lawrence Christon's interview with 
Sylvester Stallone (Oct. 28). 
</P>
<P>
Rocky and Rambo were only Stallone's adolescence; now the real man can shine on 
his own. 
</P>
<P>
LARI WOLF 
</P>
<P>
Beverly Hills 
</P>
