<HEADLINE>
<P>
MATURE TRAVELER: GOLF PACKAGE FROM TUCSON HOTEL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By HANK KOVELL 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A discount golf package for mature travelers is being offered by the Westin La 
Paloma Resort Hotel in Tucson, Ariz. 
</P>
<P>
Good through May 24, 1991, the "Seniors Golf Getaway" includes room 
accommodations, 18 holes of golf per day, cart and club rental and shoe storage 
for $117 per person, per day, based on double occupancy. Also included in the 
price is a forecaddie who accompanies the golfer and locates errant golf balls. 
</P>
<P>
Mature travelers are also offered a 15% discount in all five of the La Paloma 
restaurants, and the same discount on merchandise in the resort's golf and 
tennis shops. The golf package usually sells for $760 for two people for two 
nights. 
</P>
<P>
The Westin has a 27-hole Jack Nicklaus golf course, tennis courts, health and 
fitness center and pool. The discount is offered to mature travelers over age 
55 or members of AARP. For more information or reservations, call (800) 
876-3683, or write to Westin La Paloma Resort Hotel, 3800 E. Sunrise Drive, 
Tucson, Ariz. 85718. 
</P>
<P>
An elegant little hideaway, the Empress Hotel in La Jolla, is offering a 10% 
discount on a space-available basis for mature travelers who are members of 
AARP. The discount is valid at any time. The Empress is located in the heart of 
La Jolla, within easy walking distance of La Jolla's main shopping district, 
galleries and museums. 
</P>
<P>
Regular rates (before discount) for one or two guests run from $120 to $170 per 
night for guest rooms and $250 to $325 for suites with spa and kitchenette. 
Also included in the package are airport pickup, daily newspaper, refrigerators 
stocked with complimentary soft drinks and coffee in the rooms. 
</P>
<P>
For reservations or more information, call (800) 525-6552 or write to the 
Empress Hotel, 7766 Fay Ave., La Jolla, Calif. 92037. 
</P>
<P>
A mature traveler winter discount program is again being offered by Oakwood 
Resort Apartments, which includes 60 apartment complexes throughout the United 
States. 
</P>
<P>
Daily rates are $19 to $41, depending on location -- a discount of as high as 
33% in some cases. Oakwood provides full-size studios and one- and two-bedroom 
apartments furnished with linens, silverware, glass and dinnerware, color TV 
and weekly maid service. All units have complete kitchens with stove and 
refrigerator and are supplied with cooking utensils. 
</P>
<P>
Oakwood Apartments are located throughout California and in Texas, Denver, Las 
Vegas and Orlando, Fla. Other Eastern sites include Washington, D.C., Atlanta 
and Raleigh, N.C. 
</P>
<P>
All complexes are surrounded by landscaped grounds, and some have mini-markets, 
laundry/dry cleaners and car-rental agencies. Minimum age to qualify for the 
discounts is 55. For a directory of the properties, full-color brochure and 
information, call (800) 421-6654 or write to Oakwood Apartments, 2222 Corinth 
Ave., Los Angeles 90064. 
</P>
</TEXT>
