<HEADLINE>
<P>
GRANT TO BUY EQUIPMENT FOR COMPUTER TRAINING 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
LONG BEACH 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Community Rehabilitation Industries has received $10,000 from the Knight 
Foundation to buy adaptive equipment for its computer training program for 
people who are visually impaired. Individuals in the program are trained in 
word processing, Lotus 1-2-3 and MS Dos. 
</P>
