apartment complex that sustained $7 million in damage. ; Photo, About 240 
firefighters fought the $7-million fire into the night. BOB CAREY / Los Angeles 
Times; Photo, Onlookers gather atop a nearby hill Saturday to watch as fire 
sparked by a plumber's torch rages through much of the 544-unit complex. PERRY 
C. RIDDLE / Los Angeles Times 
