<GRAPHIC>
<P>
Photo, Scenic Route: A man and his daughter are dwarfed by trees while 
strolling through Libbey Park in Ojai. ALAN HAGMAN / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
<TYPE>
<P>
